text: Compsosoma mniszechii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1857. It is known from Brazil and Peru.BioLib.cz - Compsosoma mniszechii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1857
